&gt; Specification&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://wicg.github.io/ua-client-hints/#sec-ch-ua-form-factor"&gt;https://wicg.github.io/ua-client-hints/#sec-ch-ua-form-factor&lt;/a&gt;
