&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; sites of `navigator.permissions.query()` that isn't catching errors,
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; since
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; that will throw a TypeError and can break a page.
