&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&q=date:20240221" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 21 Feb 2024 08:03:51 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
